cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with generating 3D scenes with multiple objects using generative models and convolutional neural networks. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of auto-encoders and adversarial training, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
